# Applies only to builds whose `context:` is playground-v2/ (the host images —
# see hosts/Dockerfile — and the cmdb stub which needs hosts/inventory.yaml).
# Services with scoped contexts (./keycloak, ./squid, ./unbound, ./zeek,
# ./threat-intel, ./change-mgmt) have their own context roots and are unaffected.
#
# Root-context builds only need hosts/, cmdb/, and keycloak/realm.yaml.
# Everything else is noise.
*
!hosts/
!hosts/**
!cmdb/
!cmdb/**
!keycloak/realm.yaml
